tion to open Call To Action buttons in an iframed lightbox.</li>\r\n<li>Feature - Added option to include \'%portfolio_category%\' in portfolio item detail slug.</li>\r\n<li>Feature - Updated LayerSlider to version 4.5.5 (new 3d transitions)</li>\r\n<li>Feature - The [image] shortcode now has a parameter labeled \"newWindow\" in order to open the image/url in a new window or tab.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Added visual parent/child relationship in slider, blog and portfolio categories in admin panel.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Independent WP [gallery] now display in independent lightbox groups.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug where the top dropdown menu would stay behind YouTube videos.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Included \"First\" and \"Last\" strings in the theme translation.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Updated the Twitter widget and shortcode in order to use the v1.1 API with OAuth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<h4>1.4 - 04/03/2013</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Feature - You can now display a sidebar in portfolio item detail pages (first enable this feature in the \"Theme Options » Portfolio\" tab).</li>\r\n<li>Feature - Option to toggle opening a portfolio item in a new window/tab.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Added backwards support to jQuery.browser and several other minor tweaks for future compatibility with jQuery 1.9+</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Prevented the lightbox from appending \"#prettyPhoto\" to the URL when clicking a lightbox thumbnail.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed compatibility with the new version of the SublimeVideo player (unfortunately the FLV file format was dropped so references to this format were removed from the admin panel).</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Added the \"Other Work\" and \"Other Posts\" strings to the default.po language file.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Current page link color on the superior-header right area should now be visible.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug on the sub-header title not being properly aligned to the left when using an image background.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug that prevented blog posts from being properly rendered if the WordPress resize function failed.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug that deleted all custom sidebars when deleting a single custom sidebar in Webkit browsers.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug that prevented upload field from working properly in the pages, posts, slider items and portfolio items custom settings.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Tabs should no longer overlap if there isn\'t enough horizontal space, they should stack instead.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Prevented errors in Google Rich Snippets.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Theme normal sliders with one element only should now hide the slider navigation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Version Diff:</strong> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_4.jpg\">http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_4.jpg</a>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<h4>1.3 - 17/01/2013</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Feature - Added a new [testimonial_scroller] shortcode in order to rotate testimonials inside the same container. (<a href=\"http://vanguard.unispheredesign.com/features/shortcodes/testimonials/\">demo</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Feature - Added a new [logo_scroller] shortcode in order to display a scrolling list of client logos. (<a href=\"http://vanguard.unispheredesign.com/features/shortcodes/logo-scroller/\">demo</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Feature - Added a new [accordion] shortcode. Visually it\'s the same as the [toggle] shortcode, only adds a mutually exclusive behavior to toggles inside the accordion. (<a href=\"http://vanguard.unispheredesign.com/features/shortcodes/toggles-and-tabs/\">demo</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Feature - You can now individually assign a global custom background color to the sub-header bar with solid background.</li>\r\n<li>Feature - There\'s a new admin option where you can hide the breadcrumbs.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Removed the appending hash code to the URL when viewing pages with the AddThis social share buttons.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - When creating new pages or posts, the sub-header bar with solid background is selected by default.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Updated the LayerSlider plugin to the latest 3.6.2 version.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug that prevented the mobile dropdown menu from being clickable in certain situations.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed displaying [gallery] shortcodes in WordPress 3.5 when the images weren\'t attached to the page or post.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed the styling of portfolio items and post widgets shortcode inside the [wide_bar] shortcode.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug that prevented blog and portfolio post widget shortcodes from displaying columns correctly inside pages with sidebar.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed styling issues in the footer widgets are where some elements add the text color equal to the background color.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed shortcodes not being parsed in the LayerSlider custom content.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed [tab] shortcode styling in small screen sizes.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed a bug preventing page content from displaying in the blog page templates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Version Diff:</strong> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_3.jpg\">http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_3.jpg</a>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<h4>1.2 - 20/12/2012</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Feature - Added an option to the Twitter widget and shortcode to use JavaScript in order to retrieve tweets in the client side. This is useful when your site is on a shared hosting environment and the Twitter API is limited resulting in no tweets.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Removed the defined position in which the Vanguard admin panel appears on the WordPress admin area, which was preventing some plugin menus from appearing.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Made the breadcrumbs \"You are here\" string available for translation.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed the styling of WPML language changer widget in dropdown menu mode when added to the superior-header or the footer bar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Version Diff:</strong> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_2.jpg\">http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_2.jpg</a>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<h4>1.1 - 13/12/2012</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Feature - Added the option of adding single post \"previous\" and \"next\" navigation below the post content (also available on the portfolio items).</li>\r\n<li>Feature - You now have the option in a per post basis of not displaying the title and meta info overlayed on the image in the wide blog template and single post page.</li>\r\n<li>Feature - Added a PSD file containing some pages of the theme design.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - Some admin panel buttons and select fields were displaying incorrectly after the WordPress 3.5 update.</li>\r\n<li>Tweak - If you manually set a post excerpt it will now properly override the post summary on the blog list pages.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Fixed the \"Update\" Google Web Fonts button in the Fonts Manager.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - The YouTube and Vimeo videos were not properly resizing to their parent content area.</li>\r\n<li>Fix - Sub-headers with image backgrounds now properly resize according to the device\'s width.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Version Diff:</strong> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_1.jpg\">http://notifier.unispheredesign.com/vanguard/diff_1_1.jpg</a>\r\n]]>\r\n	</changelog>\r\n</notifier>','no'),(506,'_transient_timeout_presstrends_data','1375416503','no'),(507,'_transient_presstrends_data','a:14:{s:3:\"url\";s:16:\"technotalent.com\";s:5:\"posts\";i:0;s:5:\"pages\";s:2:\"43\";s:8:\"comments\";i:0;s:8:\"approved\";i:0;s:4:\"spam\";i:0;s:9:\"pingbacks\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"post_conversion\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"theme_version\";s:3:\"1.3\";s:10:\"theme_name\";s:33:\"Vanguard (shared on wplocker.com)\";s:9:\"site_name\";s:12:\"TechnoTalent\";s:7:\"plugins\";i:3;s:6:\"plugin\";s:88:\"Akismet%26Hello+Dolly%26LayerSlider+WP%26MailChimp%26Revolution+Slider%26WP+Retina+2x%26\";s:9:\"wpversion\";s:5:\"3.5.2\";}','no'),(558,'_tr