pertise not available internally</li>\r\n	<li>Temporary support during expansion or staff reorganization</li>\r\n	<li>Assistance in meeting critical deadlines</li>\r\n	<li>Impartial analyses of your technology or workflow</li>\r\n	<li>Fresh thinking or a change in direction</li>\r\n	<li>Training and knowledge transfer to upgrade your in-house staff\'s skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','IT Consulting Services','','publish','open','open','','it-consulting-services','','','2013-07-31 19:39:37','2013-07-31 19:39:37','',22,'http://technotalent.com/?page_id=27',0,'page','',0),(28,1,'2013-07-31 19:39:27','2013-07-31 19:39:27','<h1></h1>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h2>Short-term IT Staffing for Big-time Challenges</h2>\nProject One\'s temporary IT staffing and IT consulting services help clients who need:\n<ul>\n	<li>Specialized expertise not available internally</li>\n	<li>Temporary support during expansion or staff reorganization</li>\n	<li>Assistance in meeting critical deadlines</li>\n	<li>Impartial analyses of your technology or workflow</li>\n	<li>Fresh thinking or a change in direction</li>\n	<li>Training and knowledge transfer to upgrade your in-house staff\'s skills</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>','IT Consulting Services','','inherit','open','open','','27-revision','','','2013-07-31 19:39:27','2013-07-31 19:39:27','',27,'http://technotalent.com/?p=28',0,'revision','',0),(29,1,'2013-07-31 19:40:03','2013-07-31 19:40:03','<h1><span style=\"font-size: 1.285714286rem; line-height: 1.6;\">Add Top IT Talent to Your Team</span></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nIf you\'re expanding or upgrading your workforce, Project One can provide you with high-performing full-time staff. We place high-talent people at all levels, from skilled technicians to senior executives.\r\n\r\nOur recruiters work with you to understand your business and technology goals, your corporate culture and position requirements. Through careful screening and skills evaluation, we select the best candidates for your review.\r\n\r\n</div>','Direct Placement','','publish','open','open','','direct-placement','','','2013-07-31 19:40:03','2013-07-31 19:40:03','',22,'http://technotalent.com/?page_id=29',0,'page','',0),(30,1,'2013-07-31 19:39:57','2013-07-31 19:39:57','<h1></h1>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h2>Add Top IT Talent to Your Team</h2>\nIf you\'re expanding or upgrading your workforce, Project One can provide you with high-performing full-time staff. We place high-talent people at all levels, from skilled technicians to senior executives.\n\nOur recruiters work with you to understand your business and technology goals, your corporate culture and position requirements. Through careful screening and skills evaluation, we select the best candidates for your review.\n\n</div>\n</div>','Direct Placement','','inherit','open','open','','29-revision','','','2013-07-31 19:39:57','2013-07-31 19:39:57','',29,'http://technotalent.com/?p=30',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2013-07-31 19:40:29','2013-07-31 19:40:29','<h1><span style=\"font-size: 1.285714286rem; line-height: 1.6;\">Hire an All-Star Team</span></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nWhen you need to staff a project quickly with multiple hires, count on Project One Team Staffing to deliver the right team.\r\n\r\nProject One supplies you a complete project team of IT consultants whose members have synergy and complementary skills. Headed by a project manager/leader, we provide expert technicians and other business and technical staff best suited to your needs.\r\n\r\nOur team remains on your project from concept to completion. Individual skill sets may vary based on the project phase. As always, we monitor our consultants\' progress and handle issues before they arise.\r\n<h2>Advantages of Project One\'s Team Staffing service:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimizes the consultant procurement and recruitment burden</li>\r\n	<li>Increases recruiting quality and consistency – ensuring the team has complementary skills and synergy</li>\r\n	<li>Project administration is provided at no additio