li><strong>Background checks</strong>. We\'re not done yet. Upon candidate selection, we run a pre-employment background check that includes criminal background, credit, motor vehicle and other appropriate checks. We also screen for illegal substance abuse.</li>\n</ol>\n<strong>And that\'s how you get the right fit every time</strong>. Because our stringent screening eliminates mismatches, we confidently send you just 2-3 candidates per opening\n\n</div>\n</div>','Ensuring the Fit','','inherit','open','open','','47-revision','','','2013-07-31 19:43:37','2013-07-31 19:43:37','',47,'http://technotalent.com/?p=48',0,'revision','',0),(49,1,'2013-07-31 19:44:58','2013-07-31 19:44:58','<h1>Job Satisfaction and Performance = Winning Results</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nProductive consultants lead to successful outcomes and satisfied clients. Project One\'s consultant relations program ensures job satisfaction and peak performance. The individuals we send you:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remain focused on their IT jobs</li>\r\n	<li>Exceed performance expectations</li>\r\n	<li>Are loyal and committed to completing your projects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>We invest in the success of our people</strong>. Our technical staff is well trained, focused on the client and rewarded for their achievements.\r\n\r\nWhen you need elite talent from out of town, we manage travel logistics. We coordinate housing, so relocation issues don\'t affect the project. We help consultants transition into their new projects, and provide them support all through its duration.\r\n\r\nThe support we provide is one of the reasons <strong>proven performers stay with Project One</strong>. Our employee retention rate is among the highest in the indu\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Peak Performance','','publish','open','open','','peak-performance','','','2013-07-31 19:44:58','2013-07-31 19:44:58','',44,'http://technotalent.com/?page_id=49',0,'page','',0),(50,1,'2013-07-31 19:44:50','2013-07-31 19:44:50','','Peak Performance','