ead. With knowledge of your upcoming requirements, we proactively begin recruitment to ensure you’ll have qualified candidates to choose from when new projects start.\r\n<h2>We quickly find the candidates other firms can\'t</h2>\r\nWe’ve been placing IT professionals and delivering staffing solutions for over two decades, and our network has been growing ever since. Our senior recruiting staff is extremely well connected and resourceful. We often present talented candidates who aren\'t typically in the job market but who\'s interest has been aroused as a result of our ability to passionately represent you and your opportunity. We optimize your time investment in IT recruitment. We carefully screen all candidates, so you don\'t have to. First we pre-screen candidates for people skills. Second we screen for technical &amp; business skills. Third we screen for your company culture fit. Finally we conduct reference checks. Out of a large pool of prospective candidates, we send you only 2-3 per opening. The consultants we recommend will always have the right mix of technical, business and people skills for your specific needs.\r\n<h2>We are proactive, available and accountable</h2>\r\nClients consistently praise our account management involvement; we are in touch at the beginning, during and in between assignments. We contact you in the way that fits your work style best, through onsite visits, phone calls and emails. As we learn more about your objectives, we anticipate your technology needs and help you plan your staffing requirements. Our consultants always hear from us too. We keep in constant touch throughout each project, so we\'re able to spot potential issues and resolve them before they arise. Through our extensive efforts, we add value to our clients\' businesses. They have responded by continuing to rely on us, many for more than 10 years and hundreds of positions filled.\r\n\r\nWe\'d be pleased to demonstrate how our methodology can help your business. Fill out the form below to contact us today.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Client Commitment','','publish','open','open','','client-commitment','','','2013-07-31 19:46:45','2013-07-31 19:46:45','',0,'http://technotalent.com/?page_id=59',0,'page','',0),(60,1,'2013-07-31 19:46:34','2013-07-31 19:46:34','','Client Commitment','','inherit','open','open','','59-revision','','','2013-07-31 19:46:34','2013-07-31 19:46:34','',59,'http://technotalent.com/?p=60',0,'revision','',0),(61,1,'2013-07-31 19:47:24','2013-07-31 19:47:24','<h1>How Project One IT Consulting is Different</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ol start=\"1\">\r\n	<li><strong>It\'s not just technology... we have industry &amp; applications expertise.</strong>\r\nOther firms tend to limit their focus and screening to resume buzzwords and neglect the importance of conceptual understanding.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>We have senior recruiters working in house. </strong>\r\nOther firms hire junior-level and offshore recruiters to cut costs &amp; save money – but the only thing this cuts is service!</li>\r\n	<li><strong>We have a tremendous 25+ year referral network to bring you fresh candidates that come highly recommended.</strong>\r\nOther firms primarily rely on job boards to send you the same candidate you can find yourself.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Our recruiting approach is “best-fit\" vs. \"first-fit” – we perform in-depth screening so we don\'t waste your time.</strong>\r\nOther firms rush to submit lots of resumes hoping to get lucky; you end up doing their screening for them! We do the job match, the skills match, the people match!</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Our proactive account management... we remain actively involved from startup orientation to resolving potential problems before they arise. </strong>\r\nOther firms take a “no news is good news” approach, disappear when problems occur and only call upon you for additional business.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nProject One\'s services go beyond staffing. We offer complimentary advisory services 